item.title: Twin Reports Indicate Oceans May Rise Higher & Much Faster
item.description: Two joint studies are out this week and indicate that the United Nations’ Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change (IPCC) 2013’s predictions of a global sea rise of a bit over 3 feet by the end of the century could be way off.
